                    <p><i class="fa-solid fa-handshake text-indigo-400 mr-1"></i> Letakkan <strong class="text-slate-300">Spikeferose (Tombak) 📌</strong> tepat di depan <strong class="text-amber-400">Wallferose 🌵</strong> agar zombie terus tertusuk saat menggigit!</p>
                </div>

                <!-- Wave Progress Bar ala PvZ -->
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3 w-full sm:w-80">
                    <span class="text-xs font-bold text-slate-300 uppercase tracking-widest font-game">PROGRESS:</span>
                    <div class="relative w-full bg-slate-950 h-5 rounded-full border-2 border-amber-800 p-0.5 overflow-hidden">
